descriptionNullable:
### Context

Malicious Drones carry dangerous loads and are harmful. So, it is crucial to distinguish between malicious drones and other flying objects.



### Content

The dataset contains five classes named Aeroplane, Bird, Drone, Helicopter, and Malicious Drone.

### Credits

If someone uses this dataset or any portion of the dataset, he/she must give credit by citing related articles.
[1] Jamil, S., Rahman, M., Ullah, A., Badnava, S., Forsat, M., & Mirjavadi, S. S. (2020). Malicious UAV detection using integrated audio and visual features for public safety applications. Sensors, 20(14), 3923.
[2] Jamil, S., Abbas, M. S., & Roy, A. M. (2022). Distinguishing Malicious Drones Using Vision Transformer. AI, 3(2), 260-273.
